The characteristics of L&D category ID for Electronic Birth Certificate information.


May contain organization-specific values: Yes


 Category Entries: 


Induction of labor


Augmentation of labor


Non-vertex presentation


Steroids for fetal lung maturation received by the mother prior to delivery


Antibiotics received by the mother during labor


Clinical chorioamnionitis diagnosed during labor or maternal temperature >= 38 C


Moderate/heavy meconium staining of the amniotic fluid


Fetal intolerance of labor


Epidural or spinal anesthesia during labor
